title: Macron fears 'worst is yet to come' from Putin after tense phone call - Fox News
content:

description: French President Emmanuel Macron said he’s convinced the "worst is yet to come" from Russian President Vladimir Putin after a tense 90-minute call between the two leaders Thursday about the war in Ukraine, according to reports.
